snippet.title: SHEEPO Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Sheepo on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1281790/SHEEPO/

Sheepo is a pacifistic shape-shifting metroidvania coming to Steam for PC on August 26th 2020.

Developed by Kyle Thompson with Music by Eric Thompson
